'''Noso Hachimangu''' (曩祖八幡宮) is a {{ill|Shinto shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinto shrine|qq=}} in {{ill|Iizuka City|ja|飯塚市|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iizuka City|qq=}}, Fukuoka Prefecture, Japan. It is a former {{ill|Prefectural shrine|ja|県社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Prefectural shrine|qq=}} and currently listed as a {{ill|Betsu Hyōsha|ja|別表神社|1=Beppyo Shrine|2=ja|3=別表神社|4=simple|5=Beppyo shrine|6=zh|7=別表神社|8=mr|9=बेप्प्यो तीर्थ|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Betsu Hyōsha|13=User:Immanuelle/Beppyo Shrine|qq=}} under the {{ill|Association of Shinto Shrines|ja|神社本庁|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Association of Shinto Shrines|qq=}}. The shrine was previously known as "Noso-no-Miya" (納祖宮).

